item.description: Introduce Keras is a high-level neural networks API, written in Python and capable of running on top of TensorFlow, CNTK, or Theano.Keras is compatible with: Python 2.7-3.6. Keras 2.2.5 was the last release of Keras implementing the 2.2.* API. It was the last release to only support TensorFlow 1 (as well as Theano and CNTK).
